'''八氟合氙(VI)酸亚硝酰'''（{{chem|(NO)|2|XeF|8}}），是由[[亚硝酰离子|亚硝酰离子]]（NO<sup>+</sup>）与八[[氟|氟]]合[[氙|氙]](VI)酸根离子（XeF<sub>8</sub><sup>2−</sup>）结合而成的化合物。其中 XeF<sub>8</sub><sup>2−</sup> 离子为[[方形反稜柱分子構型|方形反稜柱分子構型]]，Xe-F 键长分别为 1.971 Å、1.946 Å、1.958 Å、2.052 Å 和 2.099 Å。<ref>{{Cite journal en
| first1 = W. | last1 = Peterson
| first2 = H. | last2 = Holloway
| first3 = A. | last3 = Coyle 
| first4 = M. | last4 = Williams
| title = Antiprismatic Coordination about Xenon: the Structure of Nitrosonium Octafluoroxenate(VI)
| volume = 173
| journal = Science (New York, N.Y.)
| issue = 4003
| pages = 1238–1239
| issn = 0036-8075
| pmid = 17775218
| doi = 10.1126/science.173.4003.1238
|date=Sep 1971}}</ref>它可通过[[六氟化氙|六氟化氙]]与[[亚硝酰氟|亚硝酰氟]]反应制取。<ref>Cotton (2007). ''Advanced Inorganic Chemistry'' (6th ed.). Wiley-India. p. 588. ISBN 8126513381.</ref>

:{{chem|XeF|6}} + 2 NOF → {{chem|(NO)|2|XeF|8}}

类似化合物还有八氟合氙(VI)酸的碱金属盐类，例如 Cs<sub>2</sub>XeF<sub>8</sub> 和 Rb<sub>2</sub>XeF<sub>8</sub>，它们在400°C以下都是稳定的。<ref name="chandra">Chandra, Sulekh (2004). ''Comprehensive Inorganic Chemistry''. New Age International. p. 308. ISBN 8122415121.</ref><ref name="holleman1">Holleman, A. F.; Wiberg,, E. (2001). ''Inorganic Chemistry''. San Diego: Academic Press. ISBN 0-12-352651-5.</ref>

